        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "# Practical Systems — Episode\n## On-Call That Doesn't Break People\nHost: Ethan\nGuest: Priya\nEthan: Welcome back to Practical Systems.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
